296
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:18,640
Boss.

297
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,720
I'm done with my coffee. Check, please.

298
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,230
No need.

299
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:22,960
This cup is on me.

300
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:24,460
This...

301
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:27,240
You're lucky. It's free today.

302
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:29,440
Thank you, boss.

303
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:31,250
I've always had good luck.

304
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:32,990
I'll be leaving then.

305
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:05,840
Lingling.

306
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:08,420
Is that you?

307
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,720
You must have suffered a lot.

308
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:40,490
It shares its good luck
with the human world.

309
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:43,000
We should give our tenderness back

310
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,910
to our silent companions.

311
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:46,510
After all,

312
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,320
who can be certain

313
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:51,120
if we are taming them

314
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:53,750
or being saved

315
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:56,120
by them?

316
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:00,870
Lingling.

317
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,240
I'm back.

318
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:06,390
I finally found you.

319
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,600
I'll take you home right now.

320
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,390
I'll never let you wander again,

321
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:11,870
okay?

322
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,890
A reunion after a long time.

323
00:16:19,030 --> 00:16:19,830
In the future,

324
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:21,720
this boy will definitely give his blessing

325
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:22,920
to the God of Fortune.

326
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:24,830
He will protect it for a lifetime

327
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:27,480
and bring it happiness and health.

328
00:16:28,820 --> 00:16:30,020
I'm a little touched.

329
00:17:08,589 --> 00:17:10,349
Ya, why are you up?

330
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,410
You need to rest. Come here.

331
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,550
Where am I?

332
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:23,960
My home.

333
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,109
Your home?

334
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,580
How are you feeling right now?

335
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,350
Not so good.

336
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:34,000
Maybe I should go to the hospital.

337
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:35,240
There is no need.

338
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,510
When you were unconscious,

339
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:38,240
I already had a doctor check on you.

340
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:38,640
Ya,

341
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,550
you're pregnant.

342
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:43,100
I'm pregnant?

